overview: What is it about the insatiable Misty Rain that makes her one of the most popular stars in the business? Is it her sleek physique? Her sultry smile? Her voracious appetite for pure, unadulterated, wild sex? Or is it simply a certain je ne se quois that makes her so darn desirable? Whatever the reason, you'll be sure to enjoy this raunchy retrospective of her finest performances, hand-picked and hosted by Mister herself, along with a brand-new climatic fantasy scene custom maid from Ms. Rain's own personal specs.
title: Deep Inside Misty Rain
